<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.scribd.com/doc/13030408/-Shrimadbhagwat-Gita" class="external text" title="http://www.scribd.com/doc/13030408/-Shrimadbhagwat-Gita" rel="nofollow">Original Sanskrit text with Hindi Translation</a> by <a href="/wiki/Gita_Press" title="Gita Press">Gita_Press</a></li>
